:: Action {"position":"3600,800","size":"100,100"}
I squeeze the trigger, and a single shot rings out.
Everyone in a two hundred foot radius flinches.

(if: $tookShot is false or $focus <= 0)[(if: $focus <= 0)[But as I pull the trigger, my eyes darted over to the little girl, so sweet and innocent, uncorrupted by the world. It's only for the briefest of milliseconds, but that's all it takes.

]The shot misses the man cleanly. The concrete path in front of him explodes as the bullet strikes it.](else:)[His body ragdolls as the impact of the shot throws him five or six feet forward.

I see the child.]

[[Continue...->Aftermath]]


:: Aftermath {"position":"3800,800","size":"100,100"}
(if: $tookShot is false or $focus <= 0)[Without a second's hesitation, the man grabs his daughter and breaks for the SUV he arrived in. He nearly rips the door off its hinges, throws his daughter inside, and leaps in after her.

The SUV takes off and I quickly lose visual.](else:)[
Confused, she turns to where the man was just standing.
As she turns, I get a glimpse of her face. The blood splatter got her good. It's dripping down her face and on to the pavement.

Her shirt and pants, once pink and blue respectively, are now the same deep shade of red.

She looks down at what is now a lifeless corpse.
I read the words off her lips.

"Daddy?"]

[[My phone buzzes.|MissionResult]]


:: CallBoss {"position":"2400,800","size":"100,100"}
I pull back from my rifle for the first time in fifteen minutes, pull out my phone, and dial Boss.

It rings.
It rings again.
It rings a third time, and then...

Silence.

[[Boss?->PhoneCall1]]


