:: Focus {"position":"1200,800","size":"100,100"}
I try to slow my breathing and focus, though the sizzling air is working tirelessly against me. Checking my pulse, it's a tad higher than the ideal sixty beats per minute, instead hovering at around seventy-five. Damn.

[[Can't screw this one up, Rohan.|TimeCheck]]


:: Height {"position":"1200,1000","size":"100,100"}
I look down toward the asphalt grid below. It's a long way down. Thirty stories at least. Not great. I'd like to avoid a repeat of Budapest if possible. Shit got out of hand real quick back then.

[[Continue...|TimeCheck]]


