:: Meandering {"position":"1600,800","size":"100,100"}
Minutes pass, and while waiting I notice all the parkgoers happily going about their day. Some are with their partners, some are pushing strollers, and some are sitting sipping iced tea. Pity. None of them have any idea that the entire park is about to be an active crime scene. Oh well, used to be me. Before all this.

And as if on cue, the red SUV pulls up to the park. The left rear passenger door opens, and out steps our man. I lock my aim to his forehead as he walks around the vehicle. Easy shot. But then, he opens the right rear passenger door, and...

[[What the hell...?|Twist]] 


