:: Twist {"position":"1800,800","size":"100,100"}
...A child steps out of the vehicle. A little girl, no older than eight by the look of it. She's wearing a bright pink shirt with a yellow star on the front, navy blue jeans that drop below her ankles, and a matching denim jacket, falling equally far beyond her wrists.

She runs to the man who picks her up and, with a smile, squeezes her tight before putting her back down. He takes her hand and they start walking.

Son of a bitch brought his daughter to his own assassination.

